---
---

<div>
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="eyebrow">Target outcomes</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      What strong progress looks like
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      These are target outcomes from DEVS-style execution, not generic course
      completion claims.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="surface-card p-8">
      <p class="text-base copy-muted mb-6">
        I can run Git, review, and sprint workflows with confidence instead of guessing.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="text-xs copy-subtle font-mono">Outcome: Git + workflow confidence</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-8">
      <p class="text-base copy-muted mb-6">
        I can walk through shipped work and explain technical decisions, not just tutorial steps.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="text-xs copy-subtle font-mono">Outcome: Interview-ready project stories</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-8">
      <p class="text-base copy-muted mb-6">
        I communicate clearly in standups and reviews, and I ship with team-level expectations.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="text-xs copy-subtle font-mono">Outcome: Team-ready execution habits</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block surface-card p-8 max-w-2xl border-2 border-[var(--color-accent-2)]/30">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">
        Be a founding member
      </p>
      <p class="copy-muted mb-6">
        Join the beta cohort and help shape DEVS. You'll get early access and
        direct feedback opportunities.
      </p>
      <a href="#notify" class="btn-primary cta-glow inline-block">
        Join beta program <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
